text.tspan: Asperger syndrome prevalence in males vs. females, 2016
The share of the male versus share of the female population with Asperger Syndrome and other autistic spectrum
disorders. This does not include the specific category of 'autism'. Prevalence has been age-standardized to allow
for comparison between countries and over time.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
